---
import V3InteriorLayout from '../../layouts/V3InteriorLayout.astro';
---

<V3InteriorLayout
  title="About"
  eyebrow="Who is Maya"
  description="Discover the biography, sound and international career of award-winning electronic music artist Maya Fourteen."
  hasEsSibling
>
  <p>
    Award-winning electronic music artist Maya Fourteen moves fluidly across electronic genres,
    shaping sound through performance, production and curation. With a solid international
    audience and performances across respected stages worldwide, her presence carries depth and
    unmistakable taste.
  </p>
  <p>
    Originally from where the Amazon Basin begins, in Mato Grosso state, Brazil, Maya's sets are
    known for being emotionally driven and story-telling, blending deep, tech, organic and
    progressive elements into journeys that grow on you.
  </p>
  <p>
    Her work spans releases on renowned international labels and performances across three
    continents and over fifteen countries.
  </p>
</V3InteriorLayout>

<style>
  /* Scoped to this page's own <p> tags (Astro scopes styles to the file
     that literally writes the markup, not the receiving V3InteriorLayout
     slot) — so this can't leak into Press/Audio Sets/Video Sets/Book,
     which share the same layout but should stay left-aligned. */
  p {
    text-align: justify;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    p {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>
